So, 2024 is officially here and honestly couldn’t be more excited. 

1️⃣ Full-Time Crypto Content Creation
2️⃣ The market is healing
3️⃣ Moved to a new state to start fresh

The year is only beginning but got a lot of achievements I’d like to accomplish! 

1️⃣ Get closer with God 
2️⃣ Run my own NFT collection 
3️⃣ Get into better shape 

Truly have drifted away from The Word for way too long and think I finally found a church I enjoy attending. 

The goal is to be my own boss and making an nft collection about something I’m passionate about like “gaming” will drive me to make it happen. 

I’ve always never been a fan of the way I look but, never took any initiatives to change. I know everyone says that New Year New Me but, I want to take this serious and have a better healthier lifestyle. 

Hope y’all have a great start to 2024 and let’s keep pushing forward 🇺🇸
